{"type": "article", "id": 23808, "title": "放餐巾的木盒子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122144hXO08PbBIVQNSroF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个像积木一样的木制三角块是一个放餐巾的桌面工具，卷好的餐巾可以插入圆孔里，有固定形状的作用，也保持了整齐有序。每一个三角块都含有磁铁，颜色也不同，可以使六个小块拼成一个六角形，完全可以看成一组可玩耍的积木，增加了人和物之间的互动。设计师是萨凡纳艺术设计学院的学生，产品目前还没有生产。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122142YeRH62QdCAhtrkIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122142DNZdjTgrLhK8FtxJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122143YUJ9WjC7OMN2mKBd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071221438492XZohANKFWlU1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}